org.spleen.type

Interface CacheObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Sizeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleCacheObject

    public interface CacheObject
extends Sizeable
    Cache object Interface. Interface of cached object that implements time storage methods, object stored getter and setters, sizeable tools.

    vallance
